Package it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.objects

Class ObjectCharMutablePair<K>

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.objects.ObjectCharMutablePair<K>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectCharPair<K>, Pair<K,Character>, Serializable
public class ObjectCharMutablePair<K> extends Object implements ObjectCharPair<K>, Serializable
A type-specific mutable Pair; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
